name: UCFParkingGarageAvailability
0: ”Alexa, ask University Parking, how full are the garages?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: university parking
des:
This skill retrieves how full some of the UCF parking garages are, as reported by UCF Parking Services on their website.

Filled percentages are given for garages A, B, C, D, H, I, and Libra.
